<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="owe-vt">owe <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /əʊ/    美 /oʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>欠 (债)：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>owe sb sth (for sth) / owe sth to sb (for sth):</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She still owes her father $5,000. / She still owes $5,000 to her father.
她还欠她父亲5000美元。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>应给予：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>owe sb sth / owe sth to sb:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I owe him an apology. / I owe an apology to him.
我得向他道歉。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>应该把...归功于：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>owe sth to sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He owes his good health to his regular life.
他把自身的健康归功于生活有规律。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>These early settlers owed their survival to hard work and determination to succeed. 
这些早期的移民把他们的幸存归功于艰苦的劳动和必胜的决心。</p><footer>人教⑨ – 3</footer></div></div>